AutoPipette module

Holds the AutoPipette class.

The AutoPipette class is responsible for functions relating to the AutoPipette. This includes sending and receiving commands, managing different parameters and managing the different states of the pipette.

class AutoPipette.AutoPipette(moonraker_url, default_speed=500, servo_name='my_servo', stepper_name='lock_stepper')
